videos.description: Isaac Okoro picks off a pass and dishes to Anfernee McLemore, who throws down the one-handed jam to the delight of the home crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McLemore's slam gets Auburn fans on their feet) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: McLemore's slam gets Auburn fans on their feet

videos.description: Kira Lewis Jr. looks to have an easy layup in transition, but Devan Cambridge hustles back to reject the shot off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cambridge swats shot off glass on Auburn chasedown block) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Cambridge swats shot off glass on Auburn chasedown block

videos.description: J'Von McCormick's shot is off the mark, but Austin Wiley is there to grab the offensive board and flush home a powerful slam for Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wiley cleans up with second-chance jam) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Wiley cleans up with second-chance jam

videos.description: Kira Lewis Jr. gets a block on defense and passes ahead to John Petty Jr., who throws down the thunderous dunk in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Petty flushes tomahawk slam for Alabama) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Petty flushes tomahawk slam for Alabama

videos.description: Auburn's Isaac Okoro grabs a defensive rebound and takes it the other way, weaving through the Alabama defense for the two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Okoro goes coast-to-coast for powerful dunk) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Okoro goes coast-to-coast for powerful dunk

videos.description: Isaac Okoro loses the ball on the fast break and clutches his right hamstring, staying on the ground for several moments before being helped off the court.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's Okoro has to be helped off after apparent leg injury) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Auburn's Okoro has to be helped off after hamstring injury

videos.description: Trailing by three with under 30 seconds to play, John Petty Jr. connects on a 3-pointer to tie the game and send it to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Petty's triple ties it for Alabama late) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Petty's triple ties it for Alabama late

videos.description: J'Von McCormick draws a help defender and dishes to Austin Wiley under the hoop for the slam as Auburn beats Alabama in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wiley dunks it home as Auburn holds off Bama in OT) 2020/02/12

videos.headline: Wiley dunks it home as Auburn holds off Bama in OT
